<text top="1908" left="1217" width="943" height="45" font="font10" id="p1_t87" reading_order_no="84" segment_no="11" tag_type="text">5.  Kline,  S.J.  and  Rosenberg,  N.  An  overview  of  innovation.  In  The  Pos-</text>
<text top="1943" left="1251" width="906" height="46" font="font11" id="p1_t88" reading_order_no="85" segment_no="11" tag_type="text">itive  Sum  Strategy:  Harnessing  Technology  for  Economic  Growth.</text>
