<text top="2024" left="1233" width="658" height="38" font="font13" id="p1_t90" reading_order_no="87" segment_no="12" tag_type="text">.  Mehrabian,  A.  Silent  Messages.  Wadsworth,  1971.</text>
<text top="2056" left="1234" width="793" height="45" font="font10" id="p1_t91" reading_order_no="88" segment_no="13" tag_type="text">.  Rogers,  E.  Diffusion  of Innovations,  5th  ed.  Free  Press,  2003.</text>
<text top="2094" left="1233" width="926" height="45" font="font10" id="p1_t92" reading_order_no="90" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">.  Samson,  R.W.  Hyperjobs:  The  new  higher-level  work  and  how  to  grow</text>
<text top="2134" left="1249" width="630" height="41" font="font14" id="p1_t93" reading_order_no="91" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">into  it.  Futurist  39,  6  (Nov.—Dec.  2005),  41-46.</text>
<text top="2173" left="1216" width="941" height="41" font="font14" id="p1_t94" reading_order_no="92" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">9.  Senge,  P.,  Scharmer,  O.,  Jaworski,  J.  and  Flowers,  B.S.  Presence:  An</text>
<text top="2206" left="1250" width="907" height="45" font="font10" id="p1_t95" reading_order_no="93" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">Exploration  of Profound  Change  in  People,  Organizations,  and  Society.</text>
